**''Alnus rugosa'' (''A. incana'' isehen ''rugosa'')—Gwern brygh, Amerika Gledh Borlowenn
**''Alnus tenuifolia'' (''A. incana'' isehen ''tenuifolia'')—Gwern delmoen po menydh, Amerika Gledh north-west
